Boston Bruins Beat Canadiens 4-3 in Overtime to Win NHL Playoff Series

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-04-28T02:11:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/boston-bruins-beat-canadiens-4-3-in-overtime-to-win-nhl-playoff-series.html
The  Boston Bruins  beat the Montreal
Canadiens 4-3 in overtime in a deciding seventh game to advance
to the second round in the National Hockey League playoffs.  The Bruins will play the  Philadelphia Flyers  for a place in
the Eastern Conference finals. The Flyers beat the Buffalo
Sabres 5-2 in Game 7 of their series yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  